Package: datacollector
Title: Data Collector
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("MDA", "Abdeljawed", email = "med.dhaker.abdeljawed@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: this package collects data from web and social media
License: Free
Depends: R (>= 3.2.3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
prerequisite:
1- Download Apache Zookeeper  : https://zookeeper.apache.org/releases.html#download,
2- Start Zookeeper server instance : https://zookeeper.apache.org/doc/r3.3.3/zookeeperStarted.html#sc_InstallingSingleMode
3- Downlaod Apache Drill : https://drill.apache.org/download/ 
5- start drillbit server : https://drill.apache.org/docs/starting-drill-in-distributed-mode/
Note : the package should run in the same drillbit node
